1
00:00:08,064 --> 00:00:09,783
According to their investigation,

2
00:00:09,984 --> 00:00:11,663
Su Yunian

3
00:00:11,663 --> 00:00:13,224
excels both academically and morally.

4
00:00:13,503 --> 00:00:15,343
She's generous and open-minded.

5
00:00:15,544 --> 00:00:16,423
Her professors,

6
00:00:16,624 --> 00:00:19,064
principal, classmates, and friends

7
00:00:19,464 --> 00:00:21,023
all speak very highly of her.

8
00:00:27,424 --> 00:00:28,223
What's wrong?

9
00:00:29,944 --> 00:00:30,543
Jiasheng,

10
00:00:31,264 --> 00:00:33,383
she excels both academically
and morally.

11
00:00:33,383 --> 00:00:34,944
She's high in both IQ and EQ.

12
00:00:35,464 --> 00:00:36,584
Can you handle her?

13
00:00:40,143 --> 00:00:41,224
Keep talking smart

14
00:00:41,783 --> 00:00:42,703
and I'll cut you.

15
00:00:47,584 --> 00:00:48,904
But speaking of which,

16
00:00:50,343 --> 00:00:53,343
you turned Lin Shen into a eunuch.

17
00:00:53,504 --> 00:00:54,264
Can you

18
00:00:54,783 --> 00:00:55,663
clean the mess?

19
00:00:56,824 --> 00:00:57,944
Don't worry.

20
00:00:58,423 --> 00:00:59,184
I'll wipe it clean.

21
00:01:01,224 --> 00:01:01,864
Alright.

22
00:01:04,703 --> 00:01:05,783
Also, Lu,

23
00:01:06,944 --> 00:01:08,023
tell Bai Manni

24
00:01:08,944 --> 00:01:10,464
to suspend Su Yunian's shift.

25
00:01:12,104 --> 00:01:12,904
Arranging it now.

26
00:01:13,384 --> 00:01:14,703
Hello, Manni.

27
00:01:15,984 --> 00:01:17,264
Suspend someone's shift.

28
00:01:18,583 --> 00:01:19,783
Guess who?

29
00:01:20,356 --> 00:01:22,848
=The Glory Fades=

30
00:01:23,648 --> 00:01:25,888
=Episode 17=
(Dizzy)

31
00:01:26,423 --> 00:01:27,343
Why suspend me?

32
00:01:28,104 --> 00:01:29,264
What am I supposed to do?

33
00:01:29,264 --> 00:01:30,423
Just sit around all day?

34
00:01:30,544 --> 00:01:31,343
To be honest,

35
00:01:31,583 --> 00:01:32,744
I can't tell you why.

36
00:01:33,583 --> 00:01:35,503
You heard Mr. Zhao's call just now.

37
00:01:35,703 --> 00:01:36,783
It's Mr. Tu's order.

38
00:01:40,624 --> 00:01:42,343
After suspension, you're free.

39
00:01:43,264 --> 00:01:45,303
You may stay
in the lounge or dressing room.

40
00:01:45,303 --> 00:01:46,984
Or hang out at the first-floor bar.

41
00:01:47,063 --> 00:01:48,384
If you don't want to come, fine.

42
00:01:49,063 --> 00:01:49,824
Just be on standby.

43
00:01:52,984 --> 00:01:54,063
The company policy states

44
00:01:54,423 --> 00:01:56,143
for non-disciplinary suspensions,

45
00:01:56,343 --> 00:01:57,824
you'll receive a daily allowance.

46
00:01:58,744 --> 00:01:59,423
Rest assured.

47
00:01:59,984 --> 00:02:01,143
It's quite substantial.

48
00:02:02,943 --> 00:02:03,443
Then...

49
00:02:03,464 --> 00:02:05,303
But I must emphasize again.

50
00:02:06,143 --> 00:02:07,184
From now on,

51
00:02:07,984 --> 00:02:10,264
don't accept any customer's invitations.

52
00:02:13,104 --> 00:02:13,904
How long?

53
00:02:14,143 --> 00:02:14,984
Await further notice.

54
00:02:38,303 --> 00:02:39,104
Thank you.

55
00:02:51,544 --> 00:02:52,344
Thank you, Mr. Tu.

56
00:03:01,504 --> 00:03:02,064
Thank you.

57
00:03:04,544 --> 00:03:05,463
Tell me,

58
00:03:06,344 --> 00:03:07,463
why suspended my shift?

59
00:03:10,903 --> 00:03:13,183
For your own good.

60
00:03:15,384 --> 00:03:16,303
I'm all ears.

61
00:03:17,423 --> 00:03:18,224
Don't believe it?

62
00:03:19,903 --> 00:03:21,023
Then tell me.

63
00:03:21,664 --> 00:03:22,984
How is this for my own good?

64
00:03:27,984 --> 00:03:28,583
Fine.

65
00:03:29,743 --> 00:03:31,104
Since you decided to stay here,

66
00:03:31,183 --> 00:03:32,104
I won't stop you.

67
00:03:32,743 --> 00:03:33,544
Just one thing.

68
00:03:34,143 --> 00:03:35,183
Stay put.

69
00:03:35,384 --> 00:03:36,664
Keep yourself safe.

70
00:03:36,903 --> 00:03:38,104
Don't meddle in anything else.

71
00:03:42,344 --> 00:03:43,784
Ruxue, you won't believe this.

72
00:03:43,784 --> 00:03:45,583
Mr. Tu actually lit her cigarette.

73
00:03:46,703 --> 00:03:47,903
Who does she think she is?

74
00:03:48,703 --> 00:03:50,703
Are you even listening?

75
00:03:51,224 --> 00:03:51,743
Listen.

76
00:03:51,824 --> 00:03:53,944
I have something to handle.
You go ahead.

77
00:03:55,023 --> 00:03:56,023
Got it.

78
00:04:10,423 --> 00:04:11,463
Feng said,

79
00:04:11,824 --> 00:04:13,023
it must be you.

80
00:04:15,743 --> 00:04:16,863
Don't worry, Ruxue.

81
00:04:17,303 --> 00:04:17,984
I promise

82
00:04:18,344 --> 00:04:20,023
I'll handle it thoroughly.

83
00:04:30,024 --> 00:04:31,224
At the night we first met,

84
00:04:32,464 --> 00:04:33,623
you tasted A Hint of Sorrow

85
00:04:33,623 --> 00:04:34,984
and said its flavor was so-so.

86
00:04:35,423 --> 00:04:36,104
Today,

87
00:04:37,263 --> 00:04:38,423
try the Tangled Threads.

88
00:04:39,664 --> 00:04:40,464
Mr. Tu,

89
00:04:41,344 --> 00:04:42,063
perhaps

90
00:04:42,544 --> 00:04:44,104
drinks can be replicated,

91
00:04:45,024 --> 00:04:46,063
but people

92
00:04:46,544 --> 00:04:47,984
are irreplaceable.

93
00:04:48,383 --> 00:04:48,984
Right.

94
00:04:49,863 --> 00:04:51,144
Truly irreplaceable.

95
00:04:51,263 --> 00:04:53,024
I never intended to find a replacement.

96
00:04:53,704 --> 00:04:54,503
That's for the best.

97
00:04:56,104 --> 00:04:57,743
Years ago, you suspended Ruoxi's shift

98
00:04:57,743 --> 00:04:59,183
and spared her the hostess duty.

99
00:04:59,464 --> 00:05:00,263
Thank you for that.

100
00:05:00,863 --> 00:05:02,063
But I'm different.

101
00:05:02,423 --> 00:05:04,464
You know exactly why I came here.

102
00:05:04,464 --> 00:05:06,104
- So I won't...
- Try the drink first.

103
00:05:16,664 --> 00:05:17,784
It is too sweet.

104
00:05:18,743 --> 00:05:19,503
So sweet

105
00:05:20,144 --> 00:05:21,063
that one sip tells you

106
00:05:21,063 --> 00:05:22,423
it's a deliberate imitation.

107
00:05:23,943 --> 00:05:24,623
Mr. Tu,

108
00:05:24,863 --> 00:05:26,263
you understand the flavor

109
00:05:26,464 --> 00:05:27,823
of Tangled Threads best.

110
00:05:28,464 --> 00:05:30,063
Like the person who mixed this drink,

111
00:05:31,183 --> 00:05:32,823
how could she rest in peace

112
00:05:33,423 --> 00:05:34,863
over some flimsy excuse?

113
00:05:35,544 --> 00:05:37,904
You know how
to insinuate things anytime, anywhere.

114
00:05:38,823 --> 00:05:40,344
I'm just telling the truth.

115
00:05:41,183 --> 00:05:41,823
Mr. Tu,

116
00:05:43,183 --> 00:05:43,904
what about you?

117
00:05:44,823 --> 00:05:46,383
Do you like telling the truth?

118
00:05:50,263 --> 00:05:51,224
Su Yunian,

119
00:05:51,784 --> 00:05:52,823
this world

120
00:05:53,263 --> 00:05:54,943
isn't just right or wrong.

121
00:05:55,584 --> 00:05:56,743
Only kids believe

122
00:05:57,024 --> 00:05:59,104
the world is right and wrong.

123
00:06:03,623 --> 00:06:04,584
Have a drink with me.

124
00:06:05,623 --> 00:06:06,503
Don't waste it.

125
00:06:07,984 --> 00:06:08,863
Forget it.

126
00:06:09,423 --> 00:06:10,984
You know I didn't come here

127
00:06:10,984 --> 00:06:12,383
to drink.

128
00:06:12,584 --> 00:06:13,464
Besides,

129
00:06:13,623 --> 00:06:15,104
I'm in my suspension period.

130
00:06:15,623 --> 00:06:16,623
By the rules,

131
00:06:16,623 --> 00:06:18,344
I don't drink with anyone.

132
00:06:18,584 --> 00:06:19,544
Su Yunian,

133
00:06:19,704 --> 00:06:20,743
don't push it.

134
00:06:21,303 --> 00:06:22,544
Then I'll get back to work?

135
00:06:22,823 --> 00:06:23,664
Suspension's over?

136
00:06:23,823 --> 00:06:24,863
I'm not joking with you.

137
00:06:24,863 --> 00:06:25,423
I mean well.

138
00:06:25,423 --> 00:06:26,224
Do you understand?

139
00:06:26,224 --> 00:06:27,063
No.

140
00:06:27,183 --> 00:06:28,344
And I don't want to.

141
00:06:28,344 --> 00:06:29,544
Ahead lies a bottomless abyss.

142
00:06:29,544 --> 00:06:30,344
Take one wrong step

143
00:06:30,344 --> 00:06:31,224
and you'll end up

144
00:06:31,224 --> 00:06:32,024
like Ruoxi.

145
00:06:32,224 --> 00:06:33,584
Compared to uncovering the truth,

146
00:06:34,503 --> 00:06:35,584
is life that important?

147
00:06:36,024 --> 00:06:36,984
Tu Jiasheng,

148
00:06:36,984 --> 00:06:38,183
you're a coward!

149
00:06:38,784 --> 00:06:40,024
I'm not like you.

150
00:06:40,544 --> 00:06:41,823
To uncover the truth,

151
00:06:42,183 --> 00:06:43,904
I won't be stopped

152
00:06:44,144 --> 00:06:45,623
by anyone or anything.

153
00:06:46,063 --> 00:06:47,183
Excuse me.

154
00:06:59,943 --> 00:07:00,664
Yunian?

155
00:07:02,743 --> 00:07:03,383
What's wrong?

156
00:07:03,584 --> 00:07:04,144
Nothing.

157
00:07:04,263 --> 00:07:04,823
I'm leaving.

158
00:07:17,784 --> 00:07:19,743
Yunian, Mr. Tu is worried about you.

159
00:07:19,743 --> 00:07:20,743
Where are you?

160
00:07:20,904 --> 00:07:22,272
I'll pick you up with the driver.

161
00:07:22,503 --> 00:07:23,664
No need, Ms. Bai.

162
00:07:24,063 --> 00:07:24,704
Gotta go.

163
00:07:44,383 --> 00:07:45,743
- Hello, Ruxue.
- Hello, Ruxue.

164
00:08:06,704 --> 00:08:07,263
Hello.

165
00:08:09,063 --> 00:08:09,904
Is it done?

166
00:08:10,144 --> 00:08:10,984
It's done.

167
00:08:13,183 --> 00:08:14,224
Clean and efficient.

168
00:08:14,544 --> 00:08:15,383
Well done.

169
00:08:59,224 --> 00:09:00,184
Anyone there?

170
00:09:00,184 --> 00:09:01,623
Is anyone there?

171
00:09:03,503 --> 00:09:04,464
Anyone there?

172
00:09:05,064 --> 00:09:06,543
Is anyone there?

173
00:09:11,464 --> 00:09:12,743
I really don't understand

174
00:09:12,743 --> 00:09:13,863
last night's situation.

175
00:09:14,743 --> 00:09:16,263
You keep her here working,

176
00:09:16,783 --> 00:09:18,743
but you don't let her serve the guests.

177
00:09:19,903 --> 00:09:21,304
So what do you want?

178
00:09:22,263 --> 00:09:23,623
What do you feel for her?

179
00:09:26,503 --> 00:09:28,344
I just want her by my side.

180
00:09:31,424 --> 00:09:32,743
Then call her.

181
00:09:34,824 --> 00:09:36,383
Say, 'I want you by my side.'

182
00:09:37,464 --> 00:09:38,584
Problem solved, right?

183
00:09:47,424 --> 00:09:48,143
I'll call.

184
00:09:54,344 --> 00:09:56,783
Su Yunian.

185
00:09:59,968 --> 00:10:00,832
Sorry.

186
00:10:00,832 --> 00:10:03,338
The subscriber you dialed
is currently unavailable.

187
00:10:03,338 --> 00:10:04,000
Sorry.

188
00:10:12,503 --> 00:10:13,263
Who are you?

189
00:10:13,863 --> 00:10:14,704
What do you want?

190
00:10:21,424 --> 00:10:22,263
Less talk.

191
00:10:23,783 --> 00:10:24,424
So

192
00:10:25,543 --> 00:10:26,543
who exactly are you?

193
00:10:41,503 --> 00:10:42,663
My name is Qin Wei.

194
00:10:43,863 --> 00:10:45,263
Or call me by my English name,

195
00:10:45,543 --> 00:10:46,543
Carey.

196
00:10:47,984 --> 00:10:50,424
I heard you graduated
from a top university, right?

197
00:10:50,903 --> 00:10:53,663
Then you should know
the meaning of this English name.

198
00:10:53,663 --> 00:10:54,464
Carey

199
00:10:55,863 --> 00:10:57,503
means 'one who lives in a castle.'

200
00:10:58,584 --> 00:11:00,143
This is my castle.

201
00:11:02,863 --> 00:11:05,824
Welcome. Glad you could come.

202
00:11:06,224 --> 00:11:08,304
We have no grudge.
I don't even know you.

203
00:11:08,623 --> 00:11:09,863
Why are you abducting me?

204
00:11:14,424 --> 00:11:16,143
Such a pretty face.

205
00:11:16,304 --> 00:11:17,143
Look at me.

206
00:11:19,184 --> 00:11:20,064
What a pity.

207
00:11:21,543 --> 00:11:23,383
Today, I'm going to ruin it.

208
00:11:26,104 --> 00:11:27,224
Was your face

209
00:11:28,383 --> 00:11:29,584
given by your mother?

210
00:11:31,944 --> 00:11:33,184
How come it looks exactly

211
00:11:33,383 --> 00:11:34,704
like An Ruoxi's?

212
00:11:36,424 --> 00:11:38,184
Your mother sure knew
how to make a copy.

213
00:11:40,783 --> 00:11:41,584
That's right.

214
00:11:42,704 --> 00:11:44,383
We truly don't know each other.

215
00:11:44,783 --> 00:11:45,824
But there are

216
00:11:46,143 --> 00:11:47,863
people we both know,

217
00:11:48,184 --> 00:11:49,224
some loved,

218
00:11:49,424 --> 00:11:50,344
some hated,

219
00:11:50,344 --> 00:11:51,623
and some envied.

220
00:11:52,184 --> 00:11:53,424
In this world,

221
00:11:53,584 --> 00:11:54,863
relationships between people

222
00:11:54,984 --> 00:11:56,743
are never that simple.

223
00:11:58,984 --> 00:11:59,824
Isn't that right,

224
00:12:00,383 --> 00:12:01,224
baby?

225
00:12:04,263 --> 00:12:05,184
I get it now.

226
00:12:07,143 --> 00:12:08,304
It's Bai Ruxue.

227
00:12:09,424 --> 00:12:10,863
She set this up.

228
00:12:11,824 --> 00:12:12,543
(GM's Office)
Right?

229
00:12:15,824 --> 00:12:17,424
You're quite clever.

230
00:12:18,424 --> 00:12:19,584
So beautiful,

231
00:12:20,464 --> 00:12:21,503
and smart,

232
00:12:22,903 --> 00:12:25,663
no wonder you became
Mr. Tu's new favorite.

233
00:12:28,263 --> 00:12:29,903
But,

234
00:12:30,984 --> 00:12:31,984
if today,

235
00:12:33,464 --> 00:12:34,623
your face

236
00:12:35,424 --> 00:12:36,503
had a scar,

237
00:12:37,023 --> 00:12:39,023
just like mine,

238
00:12:39,424 --> 00:12:40,824
and if I pull out your nails,

239
00:12:40,824 --> 00:12:42,064
one

240
00:12:42,543 --> 00:12:43,543
by

241
00:12:44,344 --> 00:12:45,783
one,

242
00:12:46,464 --> 00:12:47,383
would Tu Jiasheng

243
00:12:47,903 --> 00:12:50,104
still fall for you?

244
00:12:53,344 --> 00:12:54,224
Qin Wei,

245
00:12:56,584 --> 00:12:57,584
let me go!

246
00:12:58,663 --> 00:13:00,023
You're committing a crime!

247
00:13:00,344 --> 00:13:01,263
This is a crime!

248
00:13:01,263 --> 00:13:02,104
Do you understand?

249
00:13:04,104 --> 00:13:05,344
You're insane!

250
00:13:05,464 --> 00:13:06,863
If I let you go,

251
00:13:06,944 --> 00:13:08,064
the crime wouldn't go away,

252
00:13:08,064 --> 00:13:09,903
and I'd become a criminal!

253
00:13:12,704 --> 00:13:14,543
Childish.

254
00:13:17,267 --> 00:13:18,049
Sorry.

255
00:13:18,272 --> 00:13:19,648
- Can't get through.
- The subscriber you dialed

256
00:13:19,648 --> 00:13:22,004
is out of the service area
for the moment.

257
00:13:22,304 --> 00:13:23,707
Please try again later.

258
00:13:24,503 --> 00:13:26,263
She never answers calls
when she's off work?

259
00:13:30,903 --> 00:13:32,064
Could she be in danger?

260
00:13:34,143 --> 00:13:36,023
What danger could our people
possibly be in?

261
00:13:37,464 --> 00:13:38,984
Was she drunk before she went

262
00:13:38,984 --> 00:13:39,783
last night?

263
00:13:44,743 --> 00:13:45,984
If you're that worried,

264
00:13:45,984 --> 00:13:47,424
just call her again.

265
00:13:47,863 --> 00:13:48,543
If no answer,

266
00:13:48,543 --> 00:13:49,623
leave a message.

267
00:13:50,224 --> 00:13:51,984
Speak to her nicely.

268
00:13:52,263 --> 00:13:53,503
Stop dragging your feet.

269
00:14:06,263 --> 00:14:07,984
Your phone actually has a signal.

270
00:14:13,584 --> 00:14:14,383
Tu Jiasheng!

271
00:14:20,143 --> 00:14:20,743
Save me!

272
00:14:21,064 --> 00:14:21,984
The abandoned factory!

273
00:14:29,312 --> 00:14:32,986
♪If the heart can't hear the sorrow♪

274
00:14:33,285 --> 00:14:36,476
♪It only makes everything look so fake♪

275
00:14:38,112 --> 00:14:41,929
♪Your eyes resemble hers too much♪

276
00:14:42,478 --> 00:14:45,277
♪Who makes me forget whom♪

277
00:14:46,748 --> 00:14:50,478
♪The warmth in my heart is fading♪

278
00:14:50,702 --> 00:14:54,199
♪Every glance feels like atonement♪

279
00:14:55,598 --> 00:14:59,285
♪Ambiguity hidden in the night breeze♪

280
00:14:59,923 --> 00:15:05,038
♪Blows away the chance to explain♪

281
00:15:05,600 --> 00:15:09,876
♪I feel guilty♪

282
00:15:10,336 --> 00:15:14,190
♪I'll have no regrets
even I leave quietly♪

283
00:15:15,054 --> 00:15:18,497
♪Even in tears♪

284
00:15:19,246 --> 00:15:23,160
♪It doesn't matter♪

285
00:15:23,342 --> 00:15:27,165
♪We embrace in dreams♪

286
00:15:28,000 --> 00:15:31,452
♪I let down all my defenses♪

287
00:15:32,544 --> 00:15:36,049
♪Though the story has its end♪

288
00:15:36,736 --> 00:15:44,160
♪I'll journey with you all my life♪
